parameters:
\nc<>I have fulfilled my mission. If it was helpful to you, then
I'm glad.

\nc<>What should we do, meow? Should we also erase this one as it
is?

\nc<>If we leave it alone, it might create more Invasoids. The
best course of action here would be to cut it down, but...
\nc<>They still don't know anything, after all.
\nc<>Hey, you. Won't you come to my place?

\nc<>If you promise not to attack people, I'll take care of you
in my own way.
\nc<>What's the matter with that child, meow?

\nc<>You can't just bring them here without permission, meow.

Quickly return them to their original place, meow!

\nc<>Please, Cashew Nut! I promise to give you a proper bath and
take you for walks!

\nc<>...What kind of joke are you trying to make? I don't need
your permission or anything.

\nc<>Hmm... well, considering they survived even after the
mother body collapsed, it might be appropriate to see them
as a separate individual, meow.

\nc<>But even so, bringing beings from another world... well, if
Kei takes responsibility properly...!

\nc<>What are you mumbling about?
Hurry up and come, or
I'll leave you behind.
\nc<>I obtained the memory T5: Extermination of the Invasoid.

\nc<>Good listeners increased by 7,000, and bad listeners
increased by 3,000.
